    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 350ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
